# Supabase Standards

- **@supabase/supabase-js** v2.98+; Node 20+ required
- Browser client in `lib/supabase/client.ts`; server client in `lib/supabase/server.ts`
- Env: `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`, `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` (server-only)
- Enable RLS on all tables; define policies per role
- Index frequently queried columns
- Generate types: `supabase gen types typescript` -> `types/database.ts`

```typescript
// client.ts
import { createBrowserClient } from "@supabase/ssr";

export function createClient() {
  return createBrowserClient(
    process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL!,
    process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY!
  );
}
```
